  <p>Government wants to link <b>N</b> rural villages in the country with <=
b>N-1</b> roads.<br>(that is a <i>spanning tree</i> with <b>N</b> vertices =
and <b>N-1</b> edges).</p><br><p>The cost to build a road to connect two vi=
llages depends on the terrain, distance, etc.<br>(that is a <i>complete und=
irected weighted graph</i> of <b>N*(N-1)/2</b> weighted edges).</p><br><p>Y=
ou want to minimize the total building cost. How are you going to build the=
